{{Infobox Government agency |agency_name = Ministry of Education and Science (Міністерство освіти і науки) |nativename = |nativename_a = |nativename_r = |logo = |logo_width = 150px |logo_caption = |seal = Ministry of Education and Science of Ukraine (en c).png |seal_width = |seal_caption = |formed = 12 December 1991 (28 June 1917) |preceding1 = Ministry of Education and Science, Youth and Sports |dissolved = |superseding = |jurisdiction = {{UKR}} |headquarters = 10 Ploshcha Peremohy, [[Kyiv]] |latd = |latm = |lats = |latNS = |longd = |longm = |longs = |longEW = |employees = |budget = |minister1_name = [[Liliya Hrynevych]] <ref name="UNIANnewcab14416">[http://www.unian.info/politics/1319232-new-cabinet-formed-in-ukraine.html New Cabinet formed in Ukraine], [[UNIAN]] (14 April 2016)</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://mon.gov.ua/about/pro-ministerstvo.html | title = Official website of the Ministry. About (In Ukrainian). | date = 2014 }}</ref> |minister1_pfo = |minister2_name = |minister2_pfo = |chief1_name = |chief1_position = |parent_agency = [[Cabinet of Ministers of Ukraine|Cabinet of Ministers]] |child1_agency = Service for intellectual property |child2_agency = Agency of Science, Innovations, and Informativeness |website = [https://mon.gov.ua Official website] {{uk icon}} |footnotes = }} [[File:Київ, пр-т Перемоги,10.JPG|thumb|270px|Headquarters of the Ministry in [[Kyiv]]]] {{Politics of Ukraine}}
The '''Ministry of Education and Science of Ukraine''' ({{lang-uk|Міністерство освіти і науки України}}) is the main body in the system of central bodies of the executive power. In 9 December 2010 – 28 February 2013 the Ministry of Education and Science led by [[Dmytro Tabachnyk]] was merged with Ministry of Youth and Sports.<ref>[http://zakon1.rada.gov.ua/laws/show/242-91-%D0%BF Declaration of Cabinet of Ministers]</ref>
On 28 February 2013 [[Ukrainian President|President]] [[Viktor Yanukovych]] reorganized the Ministry of Education and Science, Youth and Sports and the State Service for Youth and Sports, creating the Ministry of Education and Science of Ukraine and the [[Ministry of Youth and Sports (Ukraine)|Ministry of Youth and Sports]].<ref name=LIGA>{{ru icon}} [http://file.liga.net/person/587-ravil-safiyllin.html Short bio of Ravil Safiullin], Информационно-аналитический центр "ЛІГА"</ref>
==Structure <ref>{{cite web | url = http://mon.gov.ua/citizens/populyarni-zapitannya/ | title = Official website of the Ministry. FAQ (In Ukrainian). | date = 2014 }}</ref>== The ministry consists of the central body headed by [[Minister (government)|the minister]],<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mon.gov.ua/about/polozhennya-reglament-ker%D1%96vnicztvo/grinevich-liliya-mixajlivna.html | title = Official website of the Ministry. Lilia Hrynevych (In Ukrainian). | date = 2014 }}</ref> first deputy, and other deputies to assist the minister. Part of ministry elects several state administrations representatives that are specialized in certain field and coordinate operation of government companies.
